OL,4,Crapid review of child safeguarding
OL,6,FA rapid review of child safeguarding
OL,7,Fpractice has been ordered following
OL,8,Fthe death of a mother and daughter.
OL,10,FMartina Karos, 40, and Eleni Edwards,
OL,11,Feight, were found dead next to each
OL,12,Fother in what police have called a
OL,13,Fsuspected murder-suicide at their home
OL,14,Fin Salford in September 2024 .
OL,16,FAs a result Salford City Council is
OL,17,Fcarrying out the rapid review, with
OL,18,Fthe report due to be finalised by the
OL,19,Fend of July, a pre-inquest hearing
OL,20,Finto the deaths was told.
