OL,6,FThe hearing at Bolton Coroner's Court
OL,7,Fwas told an investigation into the
OL,8,Fincident is ongoing.
OL,10,FA full inquest, provisionally set for
OL,11,F12 January 2026, will look at events
OL,12,Ffrom the 18 months prior to the
OL,13,Fdeaths, which saw a decline in
OL,14,FMartina's mental health.
OL,16,FMartina Karos was brought up in Rome,
OL,17,Fof Italian and Greek descent, spoke
OL,18,Ffive languages and lived on South
OL,19,FRadford Street in Salford for several
OL,20,Fyears having studied at the University
OL,21,Fof Salford.
