OL,4,Crapid review of child safeguarding
OL,6,FIn the wake of her death, friends told
OL,7,Fof how Martina struggled with mental
OL,8,Fill-health as she cared for her
OL,9,F'severely disabled' daughter.
OL,11,FThe council, at the time, said that
OL,12,FMartina and Eleni were provided with a
OL,13,Frange of support services, but did not
OL,14,Fdisclose further details, but those
OL,15,Fwho knew her raised concerns about the
OL,16,Flevel of support offered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
