OL,6,FEleni's father, Martina's mother, and
OL,7,FEleni's second grandmother attended
OL,8,Fthe hearing, together with legal
OL,9,Frepresentatives from Greater
OL,10,FManchester Mental Health Service
OL,11,F(GMMH), Salford City Council, the
OL,12,FMedical Defence Union, and a Detective
OL,13,FChief Inspector from Greater
OL,14,FManchester Police.
