OL,4,Crapid review of child safeguarding
OL,6,FMartina's family and friends lodged
OL,7,Fconcerns that problems started for
OL,8,FMartina around 16-18 months before her
OL,9,Fdeath, and that she had been affected
OL,10,Fby the sheer volume of carers that
OL,11,Fattended the home to help with Eleni's
OL,12,Fneeds.
OL,14,F"We feel that had an impact on
OL,15,FMartina's mental health," they told
OL,16,Fthe coroner.
