OL,4,Crapid review of child safeguarding
OL,6,FThe coroner, Pete Sigee, agreed that a
OL,7,Flist of carers from the agency charged
OL,8,Fwith caring responsibilities for
OL,9,FEleni, including dates and times of
OL,10,Fvisits, should be provided to the
OL,11,Fcourt ahead of the final inquest
OL,12,Fhearing.
OL,14,FMr Sigee also determined that a jury
OL,15,Fwill not be called for the final
OL,16,Finquest hearings, with the witnesses
OL,17,Fand evidence being judged by a coroner
OL,18,Falone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
