OL,4,Crapid review of child safeguarding
OL,6,FHe added that the upcoming hearings
OL,7,Fwill treat Martina and Eleni's death
OL,8,Fjointly, as they were 'so intertwined'
OL,9,Fwith similar organisations involved,
OL,10,Fsaying: "In Eleni's inquest,
OL,11,Fconsideration will likely be given to
OL,12,FMartina's mental health in the period
OL,13,Fleading up to these deaths."
OL,15,FThe next pre-inquest hearing is set
OL,16,Ffor 28 October.
